<plot>Why do dogs behave the way they do? Why aren't dogs more like cats? Is it true they don't, as a species, have a brain in their head? FLUFFY answers none of the questions, but recounts the events, based on a true story, of why you really shouldn't be kissed by a dog. It is a delightfully funny parody filled with the true joy of dog ownership.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?198371</url></doc>
